name: pametnik u shumenu, kubrat 2 od 6 colourized remix
description: Part of a series of drawings of my favourite monument, the Monument to 1300 Years of Bulgarian History, location in Shumen Bulgaria. The cubist monument sits on top of a hill located in Shumen, and depicts the kings of Bulgaria, pictured here is kubrat. This piece is a three-way collab, the colourized version by  blissofart.tez (@blissofart on twitter), and animated remix by @TBinkiewinkie
